"Change Set:		8644Collections-ul.267Collections-ul.267:- improved SequenceableCollection >> #shuffledBy:"!!SequenceableCollection methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'ul 12/28/2009 02:02'!shuffledBy: aRandom	"Durstenfeld's version of the Fisher-Yates shuffle"	| copy | 	copy := self copy.	copy size to: 2 by: -1 do: [ :i | 		copy swap: i with: (aRandom nextInt: i) ].	^copy! !